headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Bullish on Omnicom Stock?
summary: Omnicom has underperformed the broader market over the past year, but analysts are moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: Bluefish Raises $20M to Power AI Marketing for the Fortune 500
summary: Bluefish, the leading AI marketing platform for the Fortune 500, announced a $20M Series A funding round led by NEA, with participation from Salesforce Ventures. Additional investors include Crane Venture Partners, Swift Ventures, and Bloomberg Beta, bringing total Bluefish funding to $24M within 12 months of launch. Bluefish also unveiled its new Custom AI Audiences feature, which enables brands to manage their AI performance with unprecedented granularity and precision.
